                <h1>Do You Need a Background Check to Buy a Gun?</h1>
                <p>Yes, in many states, a background check is required to buy a gun. These checks are designed to ensure that individuals with criminal histories, mental health issues, or other restricting factors cannot legally purchase firearms. It's essential to understand your state's laws, as regulations can vary significantly.</p>
